{#Variables:#}
{#- user_name: full name of the user (publisher or information owner)#}
{#- pages: array of pages#}
{#    - page: \Drupal\tieto_lifecycle_management_notifications\Data\EntityLifeCycleData object #}
{#- contact_mail: email address#}
<div>
    Hello {{ user_name }},

    The page you have published or where you are marked as an information owner is near to its expiration date.
    Please review the page, and either update and publish it again or withdraw it.
    Otherwise the page will be automatically unpublished.

    Follow the link(s) to review the pages:
    <ul>
        {% for page in pages %}
            <li>
                <a href="{{ page.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">{{ page.title }}</a>
                <span class="entity-unpublish-date">Unpublish date: {{ page.unpublishDate }}</span>
            </li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    Kind regards,
    Your Intra administrator

    In case you have questions related to this email youâ€™re welcome to contact <a
            href="mailto:{{ contact_mail }}">{{ contact_mail }}</a>
</div>
